
'''浅成岩'''，是侵入[[火成岩|火成岩]]，位于地壳的中等或较浅深度(>2 km)，矿物具有中等结晶粒度。常为{{tsl|en|porphyritic|斑岩}}纹理。岩石学中，常见为[[辉绿岩|辉绿岩]]({{tsl|en|dolerite|粗玄岩}})。<ref name="Examples">{{cite web | url=http://www.qm.qld.gov.au/Find+out+about/Rocks/Types+of+rocks#.VXrjZOK4FkQ | title=Examples of rocks with different names | accessdate=12 June 2015 | archive-date=2020-05-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200506161949/https://www.qm.qld.gov.au/Find+out+about/Rocks/Types+of+rocks#.VXrjZOK4FkQ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=http://australianmuseum.net.au/Igneous-rock-types | title=Igneous rock types - Australian Museum | accessdate=14 June 2015 | archive-date=2015-06-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150603220911/http://australianmuseum.net.au/igneous-rock-types | dead-url=no }}</ref>

